<p>here I want to trigger the update query if any one of the columns are updated. But I am getting error table table is mutating, trigger/function may not see it.</p>  <pre><code>create or replace   TRIGGER TRIGGER1      AFTER  UPDATE OF HOST_ID,ENABLED_FLAG,ACTIVE_FLAG,AGENT_COUNTER,USER_WAIT_FLAG ON  MONITOR_AGENT_STATUS    FOR EACH ROW     BEGIN update monitor_agent_status set active_flag='Y', enabled_flag='Y', agent_counter=0, user_flag='N';  END; </code></pre>